title: Green Cities, USA
name: Green Cities, USA
description: This Green Cities map is based on data from the US Mayors Climate Protection Agreement" mentioned in a June 9,  2007 Washington Post article on how local municipalities are addressing global warming. To create this map  data from Seattle.Gov's website on 527 cities (combined total population of over 66 million)  was joined with the U.S cities spatial database. The join was successful for 477 cities  covering 96% of the total population of the 527 cities  or nearly 64 million.
